(42, 4, 14, 41, 1, 14, 14, 'Galilee', 'Jesus'' Ministry in Galilee', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus'' activity in Galilee, highlighting his return and subsequent preaching. The mention of ''Galilee'' in both verses connects them thematically as pivotal moments in Jesus'' ministry.', 'theme', 0.307, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
